title: Wireless networking e-books
description:
(En-USA)

A (small) collection of usable e-books for those who want to know about wireless networking.
The e-books are: 
Mcgraw Hill Installing Troubleshooting And Repairing Wireless Networks Ebook-Lib.pdf;

John Wiley & Sons - Wireless Home Networking for Dummies.pdf;

[E-Books] OReilly - Building Wireless Community Networks.pdf.

NOTE:If you liked the e-books, buy-it, book authors also needs to eat.
